            <abstract id="ref11" label="Abstract">A collection of 41 framed photographs having to do with the aftermath of the April 16, 2007 shootings. Photographers were community members who submitted images to be considered for an exhibition at Squires' Perspective Gallery in April 2008. Collection also includes additional digital images not framed for the show.</abstract>
            <physdesc id="ref10" label="Dimensions">
                <dimensions>Each framed image is approximately 20.25 x 16.25 inches.</dimensions>
            </physdesc>            
        </did>
